title: Is the 2020 Election ‘Far From Over’?
subtitle: Even as Joe Biden had secured the majority of electoral votes in the 2020 U.S. presidential election, President Donald Trump refused to concede.
author: Jessica Lee
vclaim: As of mid-November 2020, the U.S. presidential election remained "far from over," thus enough uncertainty about the outcome remained that U.S. President Donald Trump could reasonably claim he might still be the winner.
